Hella S. Haasse, Dutch Author of ‘Tea Lords,’ Dies Aged 93, Publisher Says

-- B y   M a u d   v a n   G a a l
-- 
2011-09-30T10:54:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/hella-s-haasse-dutch-author-of-tea-lords-dies-aged-93-publisher-says.html
Hella S. Haasse, the Dutch author
of novels including “The Tea Lords,” died yesterday at the age
of 93 after a brief illness, her publisher Querido  said  on its
website today.      Born in 1918 in the Dutch East Indies, now  Indonesia ,
Haasse received awards for her work including the 1983 P.C.
Hooft Prize and the Dutch Literature Prize of 2004.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Maud van Gaal at 
 mvangaal@bloomberg.net  